doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title Your Post Has Been Removed
    style.
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
      .warning-box { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .post-content { background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 3px solid #dc3545; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  body
    .container
      .header
        h1 ⚠️ Post Removed
        p Your Post Has Been Removed from Urban Lens
      
      .content
        p Dear User,
        
        p We are writing to inform you that your post has been removed from Urban Lens for violating our community guidelines.
        
        .warning-box
          p <strong>Reason:</strong>
          p #{reason}
        
        if postContent
          .post-content
            p <strong>Removed Post Content:</strong>
            p <em>#{postContent}</em>
        
        p <strong>What this means:</strong>
        ul
          li Your post is no longer visible to other users
          li The post has been removed from all feeds and search results
          li You can still view the post in your account, but it will be marked as removed
        
        p <strong>What you can do:</strong>
        ul
          li Review our community guidelines to understand what content is allowed
          li If you believe this was a mistake, you can contact our support team
          li Create new posts that comply with our guidelines
        
        p We encourage you to continue participating in our community while following our guidelines.
        
        p If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
        
        p Best regards,<br>
          The Urban Lens Team
      
      .footer
        p © 2024 Urban Lens. All rights reserved.
        p This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.

